-- Telecom Italia Reaches Accord With Tele2 on Sale of BBned for $65 Million
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-07-16T06:20:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/telecom-italia-reaches-accord-with-tele2-on-sale-of-bbned-for-65-million.html

          
          
             Telecom Italia SpA agreed to sell
BBNed to Tele2 AB for 50 million euros, according to a statement
distributed by the Italian exchange.  
 The sale won’t have a “substantial” impact on accounts,
the company said. Morgan Stanley advised on the sale.  
          
          


  


        